1947;;Body and Soul;;American;;Robert Rossen;;John Garfield, Lilli Palmer;;film noir;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Body_and_Soul_(1947_film);;Charley Davis, against the wishes of his mother, becomes a boxer. As he becomes more successful the fighter becomes surrounded by shady characters, including an unethical promoter named Roberts, who tempts the man with a number of vices. Charley finds himself faced with increasingly difficult choices.